# shadcn/ui Component Library

This project uses **shadcn/ui** for all UI elements.

## Initialization

If shadcn/ui is not initialized in the project, use:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
```

## Installing Components

To install a specific component, use the following command format:

```bash
npx shadcn@latest add [component-name]
```

### Examples

Install the button component:
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button
```

Install multiple components at once:
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button card input
```

## Guidelines

- Always use shadcn/ui components for UI elements
- Check if a component is installed before using it
- Install new components as needed using the `npx shadcn@latest add` command
- Components will be added to `src/components/ui/` directory
